OL,5, The head of the UK's biggest business  
OL,6, group has said most bosses "secretly"  
OL,7, want all of their staff to return to   
OL,8, working in offices.                    
OL,10,FTony Danker, director-general of the   
OL,11,FCBI, said the "whole world of work" had
OL,12,F"gone crazy" since the pandemic.       
OL,14,FMany companies have changed policies on
OL,15,Fremote working since Covid restrictions
OL,16,Feased, with staff offered the chance to
OL,17,Fwork from home and offices.            
OL,19,FMr Danker said working patterns would  
OL,20,Fbe talked about "for a few years".     
